	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Election dataset 2024'[Margin], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"CountMargin", CALCULATE(COUNTA('Election dataset 2024'[Margin]))
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate]", 'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate],
			"'Election dataset 2024'[Margin]", 'Election dataset 2024'[Margin],
			"CountMargin", [CountMargin]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate]", 'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [CountMargin]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate]),
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[SortBy_DM0_0],
			0,
			'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Election dataset 2024'[Margin])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Election dataset 2024'[Margin], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(

				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Election dataset 2024'[Margin],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Election dataset 2024'[Margin]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'Election dataset 2024'[Leading Candidate], [ColumnIndex]
